ion in the relay event in Beijing 16 years ago because teammate Nesta Carter violated an anti-doping rule.\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0217714879038053e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesta_Carter\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nesta Carter\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesta_Carter\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nesta_Carter\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1872}, {\"ngram\": \"a 9/9 record\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1911}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"200m\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1951}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"a disqualification\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"the relay event\", \"from\": 1994, \"to\": 2009}, {\"ngram\": \"an anti-doping rule\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2092}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless, Bolt's aura was frightening, the likes of which had never been seen before in sprinting.\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2194, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bolt's aura\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2117}, {\"ngram\": \"the likes\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"sprinting\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The nonchalance with which he crossed the line in Beijing will never be forgotten.\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2245, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 1.0217714879038053e-12, \"text\": \"Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2008_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The nonchalance\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2210}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogo produced the run of his life to claim gold in a much-anticipated 200m event.\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2382, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"21-year-old Letsile Tebogo\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the run\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2322}, {\"ngram\": \"his life\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2334}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"a much-anticipated 200m event\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2381}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the fastest qualifier and the only man to go under 20 seconds in the semi-finals, so he was certainly expected to medal.\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only man\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"20 seconds\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2451}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2463}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 2464, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, 100m champion andAmerican superstar Noah Lyleswas the overwhelming favourite to claim gold alongside his compatriot Kenny Bednarek.\", \"from\": 2511, \"to\": 2651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2636, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kenny Bednarek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenny_Bednarek\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100m champion andAmerican superstar\", \"from\": 2520, \"to\": 2555}, {\